contrib
=======

This directory contains contributions to the SML/NJ distribution.  The
software is unsupported (by us) and there is no guarantee that they
will work. The directory includes the following:

README:     this file

emacs:	    sml-modes for editing sml source code and interacting with
	    sml under GNU emacs. 

idl:        sml remote-procedure-call protocol generator & X interface

mldata:     sml pretty-printer & pretty-printer-generator

ForML:      "Formatter for ML", a prettyprinting module by Ekkehard Rohwedder

ed-lib:	    The "Edinburgh library" developed by Dave Berry
